item.title: CVE-2023-2711|2023-06-27T13:17:18.296Z -- unknown -- ultimate%20product%20catalog
item.description: The Ultimate Product Catalog WordPress plugin before 5.2.6 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed (for example in multisite setup)
